{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id448f353c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"964"},"text":"§ 964.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Miscellaneous provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id448f353d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Earnings and profits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except as provided in section 312(k)(4), for purposes of this subpart, the earnings and profits of any foreign corporation, and the deficit in earnings and profits of any foreign corporation, for any taxable year shall be determined according to rules substantially similar to those applicable to domestic corporations, under regulations prescribed by the Secretary. In determining such earnings and profits, or the deficit in such earnings and profits, the amount of any illegal bribe, kickback, or other payment (within the meaning of section 162(c)) shall not be taken into account to decrease such earnings and profits or to increase such deficit. The payments referred to in the preceding sentence are payments which would be unlawful under the Foreign Corrupt Practices Act of 1977 if the payor were a United States person.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id448f353e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Blocked foreign income","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Under regulations prescribed by the Secretary, no part of the earnings and profits of a controlled foreign corporation for any taxable year shall be included in earnings and profits for purposes of sections 952 and 956, if it is established to the satisfaction of the Secretary that such part could not have been distributed by the controlled foreign corporation to United States shareholders who own (within the meaning of section 958(a)) stock of such controlled foreign corporation because of currency or other restrictions or limitations imposed under the laws of any foreign country.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id448f353f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Records and accounts of United States shareholders","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3540-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Records and accounts to be maintained","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may by regulations require each person who is, or has been, a United States shareholder of a controlled foreign corporation to maintain such records and accounts as may be prescribed by such regulations as necessary to carry out the provisions of this subpart and subpart G.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3541-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Two or more persons required to maintain or furnish the same records and accounts with respect to the same foreign corporation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Where, but for this paragraph, two or more United States persons would be required to maintain or furnish the same records and accounts as may by regulations be required under paragraph (1) with respect to the same controlled foreign corporation for the same period, the Secretary may by regulations provide that the maintenance or furnishing of such records and accounts by only one such person shall satisfy the requirements of paragraph (1) for such other persons.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id448f3542-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Treatment of certain branches","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3543-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this chapter, section 6038, section 6046, and such other provisions as may be specified in regulations—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3544-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a qualified insurance branch of a controlled foreign corporation shall be treated as a separate foreign corporation created under the laws of the foreign country with respect to which such branch qualifies under paragraph (2), and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3545-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" except as provided in regulations, any amount directly or indirectly transferred or credited from such branch to one or more other accounts of such controlled foreign corporation shall be treated as a dividend paid to such controlled foreign corporation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3546-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Qualified insurance branch","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of paragraph (1), the term “qualified insurance branch” means any branch of a controlled foreign corporation which is licensed and predominantly engaged on a permanent basis in the active conduct of an insurance business in a foreign country if—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3547-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" separate books and accounts are maintained for such branch,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3548-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the principal place of business of such branch is in such foreign country,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3549-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" such branch would be taxable under subchapter L if it were a separate domestic corporation, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f354a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/2/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an election under this paragraph applies to such branch.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"An election under this paragraph shall apply to the taxable year for which made and all subsequent taxable years unless revoked with the consent of the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f354b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Regulations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall prescribe such regulations as may be necessary or appropriate to carry out the purposes of this subsection.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id448f354c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Gain on certain stock sales by controlled foreign corporations treated as dividends","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f354d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"If a controlled foreign corporation sells or exchanges stock in any other foreign corporation, gain recognized on such sale or exchange shall be included in the gross income of such controlled foreign corporation as a dividend to the same extent that it would have been so included under section 1248(a) if such controlled foreign corporation were a United States person. For purposes of determining the amount which would have been so includible, the determination of whether such other foreign corporation was a controlled foreign corporation shall be made without regard to the preceding sentence.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f354e-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Same country exception not applicable","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Clause (i) of section 954(c)(3)(A) shall not apply to any amount treated as a dividend by reason of paragraph (1).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f354f-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Clarification of deemed sales","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this subsection, a controlled foreign corporation shall be treated as having sold or exchanged any stock if, under any provision of this subtitle, such controlled foreign corporation is treated as having gain from the sale or exchange of such stock.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3550-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Coordination with dividends received deduction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3551-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If, for any taxable year of a controlled foreign corporation beginning after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2017","children":[],"tail":", any amount is treated as a dividend under paragraph (1) by reason of a sale or exchange by the controlled foreign corporation of stock in another foreign corporation held for 1 year or more, then, notwithstanding any other provision of this title—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id448f3552-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the foreign-source portion of such dividend shall be treated for purposes of section 951(a)(1)(A) as subpart F income of the selling controlled foreign corporation for such taxable year,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id448f3553-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a United States shareholder with respect to the selling controlled foreign corporation shall include in gross income for the taxable year of the shareholder with or within which such taxable year of the controlled foreign corporation ends an amount equal to the shareholder’s pro rata share (determined in the same manner as under section 951(a)(2)) of the amount treated as subpart F income under clause (i), and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id448f3554-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/A/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the deduction under section 245A(a) shall be allowable to the United States shareholder with respect to the subpart F income included in gross income under clause (ii) in the same manner as if such subpart F income were a dividend received by the shareholder from the selling controlled foreign corporation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3555-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of basis or similar adjustment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this title, in the case of a sale or exchange by a controlled foreign corporation of stock in another foreign corporation in a taxable year of the selling controlled foreign corporation beginning after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2017","children":[],"tail":", rules similar to the rules of section 961(d) shall apply."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id448f3556-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a","identifier":"/us/usc/t26/s964/e/4/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Foreign-source portion","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this paragraph, the foreign-source portion of any amount treated as a dividend under paragraph (1) shall be determined in the same manner as under section 245A(c).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id448f3557-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/834/s12/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–834, § 12(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1962-10-16"},"text":"Oct. 16, 1962","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/76/1027"},"text":"76 Stat. 1027","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/172/tIV/s442/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–172, title IV, § 442(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1969-12-30"},"text":"Dec. 30, 1969","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/83/628"},"text":"83 Stat. 628","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/tX/s1065/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, title X, § 1065(b)","children":[],"tail":", title XIX, §§ 1901(b)(32)(B)(iii), 1906(b)(13)(A), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-04"},"text":"Oct. 4, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/1654"},"text":"90 Stat. 1654","children":[],"tail":", 1800, 1834; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/34/tII/s206/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–34, title II, § 206(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1981-08-13"},"text":"Aug. 13, 1981","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/95/225"},"text":"95 Stat. 225","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248/tII/s288/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248, title II, § 288(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/571"},"text":"96 Stat. 571","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647/tVI/s6129/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647, title VI, § 6129(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/3716"},"text":"102 Stat. 3716","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34/tXI/s1111/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34, title XI, § 1111(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1997-08-05"},"text":"Aug. 5, 1997","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/111/968"},"text":"111 Stat. 968","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/97/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–97, title I","children":[],"tail":", §§ 14102(c)(1), 14212(b)(4), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-22"},"text":"Dec. 22, 2017","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/2193"},"text":"131 Stat. 2193","children":[],"tail":", 2217.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id448f3558-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id448f3559-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id448f355a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Foreign Corrupt Practices Act of 1977, referred to in subsec. (a), is title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/213"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–213","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1977-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 1977","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/91/1494"},"text":"91 Stat. 1494","children":[],"tail":", which enacted sections 78dd–1 to 78dd–3 of Title 15, Commerce and Trade, and amended sections 78m and 78ff of Title 15. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1977 Amendment note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78a"},"text":"section 78a of Title 15","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id448f355b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2017—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/97/s14212/b/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–97, § 14212(b)(4)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “, 955,” after “sections 952”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e)(4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/97/s14102/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–97, § 14102(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (4)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1997—Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/34"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–34","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (e)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1988—Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/647"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–647","children":[],"tail":" added subsec. (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1982—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/248"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–248","children":[],"tail":" inserted provision that payments referred to in sentence beginning “In determining such earnings and profits” are payments which would be unlawful under the Foreign Corrupt Practices Act of 1977 if the payor were a United States person."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1981—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/34"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–34","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 312(k)(4)” for “section 312(k)(3)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1976—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1065(b), 1901(b)(32)(B)(ii), 1906(b)(13)(A), struck out “or his delegate” after “Secretary”, inserted second sentence, and substituted “312(k)(3)” for “312(m)(3)” after “provided in section”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsecs. (b), (c)(1), (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/455/s1906/b/13/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–455, § 1906(b)(13)(A)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “or his delegate” after “Secretary” whenever appearing."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1969—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/172"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–172","children":[],"tail":" inserted reference to the exception provided for in section 312(m)(3)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id448f355c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id448f355d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2017 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"h